text: Mădălina Ștefania Amăistroaie (born 9 December 2002) is a Romanian archer. Amăistroaie competed at the 2020 Summer Olympics.Mădă Amăistroaie ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian archers Category:Olympians for Romania
